retrieval.client

Class RetrievalClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • retrieval.client.RetrievalClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RetrievalClientInterface

    public class RetrievalClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements RetrievalClientInterface
    This class define a client for servers. A client can search similar pictures on multiple server. Server may be distant (host/port) or local (java object)
